review_blob: Very easy to drink. Huge head, which settled away in 2 minutes. Perhaps my nose is different, but no banana, citrus, or cloves here. Something like wild forest strawberries if it were a fruit. Tastewise one the best hefeweisse.

Dark apperance. Nice head. Easy to drink, soft, perhaps hint of sweetness. This one was better a bit better than the last fre others Ive tasted and all of them were bought at the same time from the same place. Perhaps the moon is now in different position or there is some variance in storaga temperature.
